OL,4,G2200FUps and Downs of a Handyman
OL,5,     GWhen Bob becomes a handyman in
OL,6,     Gthe quiet village of Chipping
OL,7,     GSodbury, he soon finds all his
OL,8,     Gcustomers are women. Their
OL,9,     Gendless "jobs" keep him busy and
OL,10,     Gleave Bob wondering how he'll
OL,11,     Gkeep up!
OL,12,G2350FSecrets of Sex
OL,13,     GFrom beyond the grave, a 1,000-
OL,14,     Gyear-old mummy narrates a series
OL,15,     Gof kinky tales exploring the
OL,16,     Geternal battle of the sexes in a
OL,17,     Gpsychedelic mix of cosmic
OL,18,     Gthrills, and swinging
OL,19,     Gpermissiveness.
